# ============================================================================
# Owlivion Mail - Environment Variables Example
# ============================================================================
#
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your OAuth2 credentials
# See OAUTH_SETUP.md for detailed instructions on how to get these credentials
#

# Google OAuth2 Credentials
# Get from: https://console.cloud.google.com/
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-google-client-id.apps.googleusercontent.com
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=GOCSPX-your-google-client-secret

# Microsoft OAuth2 Credentials
# Get from: https://portal.azure.com/
MICROSOFT_CLIENT_ID=your-microsoft-client-id
MICROSOFT_CLIENT_SECRET=your-microsoft-client-secret

# Optional: Gemini API Key (for AI features)
# Get from: https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=your-gemini-api-key

# ============================================================================
# IMPORTANT: Never commit the .env file to Git!
# The .env file should be in .gitignore
# ============================================================================
